<darkcolour>A6416E</darkcolour><section><title>Noun plurals</title><sectiontitle>Add &lt;I&gt;-s&lt;/I&gt; to the noun to make plurals.</sectiontitle><titlesound>ELEMGRAM_2_3_1.mp3</titlesound><text1>a handbag</text1><sound1>ELEMGRAM_2_3_2.mp3</sound1><text1a>two handbag&lt;B&gt;&lt;Font color='#A6416E'&gt;s&lt;/Font&gt;&lt;/B&gt;</text1a><text2>a wallet</text2><sound2>ELEMGRAM_2_3_3.mp3</sound2><text2a>five wallet&lt;B&gt;&lt;Font color='#A6416E'&gt;s&lt;/Font&gt;&lt;/B&gt;</text2a><titlesound2>ELEMGRAM_2_3_4.mp3</titlesound2><sectiontitle2>Some noun plurals have different endings.</sectiontitle2><text3>a watch, an address</text3><sound3>ELEMGRAM_2_3_5.mp3</sound3><text3a>two watch&lt;B&gt;&lt;Font color='#A6416E'&gt;es&lt;/Font&gt;&lt;/B&gt;, five address&lt;B&gt;&lt;Font color='#A6416E'&gt;es&lt;/Font&gt;&lt;/B&gt;</text3a><text4>a scarf, a family</text4><sound4>ELEMGRAM_2_3_6.mp3</sound4><text4a>three scar&lt;B&gt;&lt;Font color='#A6416E'&gt;ves&lt;/Font&gt;&lt;/B&gt;, two famil&lt;B&gt;&lt;Font color='#A6416E'&gt;ies&lt;/Font&gt;&lt;/B&gt;</text4a></section><section><title>&lt;I&gt;this, that, these, those&lt;/I&gt;</title><sectiontitle>Use &lt;I&gt;this, that, these&lt;/I&gt; and &lt;I&gt;those&lt;/I&gt; for objects.</sectiontitle><titlesound>ELEMGRAM_2_3_7.mp3</titlesound><text1></text1><sound1>ELEMGRAM_2_3_8.mp3</sound1><text1a>What's &lt;B&gt;&lt;Font color='#A6416E'&gt;this&lt;/Font&gt;&lt;/B&gt;? </text1a><text2></text2><sound2>ELEMGRAM_2_3_9.mp3</sound2><text2a>&lt;B&gt;&lt;Font color='#A6416E'&gt;That&lt;/Font&gt;&lt;/B&gt;'s a small mobile phone.</text2a><titlesound2>ELEMGRAM_2_3_10.mp3</titlesound2><sectiontitle2>Use &lt;I&gt;this&lt;/I&gt; and &lt;I&gt;that&lt;/I&gt; for singular nouns. Use &lt;I&gt;these&lt;/I&gt; and &lt;I&gt;those&lt;/I&gt; for plural nouns.</sectiontitle2><text3>&lt;B&gt;&lt;Font color='#A6416E'&gt;This is&lt;/Font&gt;&lt;/B&gt; a beautiful picture.</text3><sound3>ELEMGRAM_2_3_11.mp3</sound3><text3a>&lt;B&gt;&lt;Font color='#A6416E'&gt;These are&lt;/Font&gt;&lt;/B&gt; beautiful picture&lt;Font color='#A6416E'&gt;s&lt;/Font&gt;.</text3a><text4>&lt;B&gt;&lt;Font color='#A6416E'&gt;That's&lt;/Font&gt;&lt;/B&gt; an interesting book.</text4><sound4>ELEMGRAM_2_3_12.mp3</sound4><text4a>&lt;B&gt;&lt;Font color='#A6416E'&gt;Those are&lt;/Font&gt;&lt;/B&gt; interesting book&lt;Font color='#A6416E'&gt;s&lt;/Font&gt;.</text4a></section></grammar>